reviewText: Gallagher is an oldie but a goodie.
Comedy with props. Funny stuff and still very relevant even to this day.
Gallagher has waayyy better shows out there than this one ... hence the 3 stars instead of the 5 I would give many other performances.

It is old but very playable, thank goodness I still have a VCR DVD combo! Wish he had converted these classics into DVDs, because there will come a day when VHS players are no more, can't even find them at resale shops now. But love Gallagher. Someone ought to tell him to quit the raunchy sexist jokes he is using in his show and go back to the superbly creative man I knew from years ago!
This is the one where he has the bald guy do jokes for a while.
